<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4605870>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 4. — Exodeconus maritimus, flower vascularization: A, longitudinal section of mature bud, along plane indicated in H; B-L, cross sections from peduncle to apex, as indicated in A. Symbols: Blackened areas, vascular tissue; gray areas, nectary; diagonal lines, transmitting tissue. Abbreviation: d, dorsal vascular bundles; e, staminal bundle; lc, lateral petal bundle; lk, lateral sepal bundle; lo, lateral ovarian bundle; mc, median petal bundle; mk, median sepal bundle; vc, ventral vascular bundle. Scale bars: for Fig. A is a; for Figs. B-L is b." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4605870/files/figure.png" .

