        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. — Exodeconus maritimus, androecium and flower trichomes: A, eglandular trichome; B, glandular trichome; C, stamens; D-F, cross section of anther, details of the stomium and endothecium; G, cross section of anther with sterile pollen sacs. Scale bars: A, B = 2 µm; C = 3 mm; D, G = 800 µm; E, F = 10 µm. Abbreviations: e = endothecium; c = crystals; s = stomium." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4605864/files/figure.png" .

